name: Neko-chan's Club
description:
In the Neko-chan's Club, you can meet girls for any taste! Sports tennis player? Or maybe a mysterious ninja girl? Do you like an insatiable Egyptian woman..? Be careful with the last one, she hasn't seen a man for a thousand years! Become a club member with Neko-chans! (˃ᆺ˂)



Easy win:
Keyboard Сtrl+D - Complete Level

FEATURES

  • 🐾 Beautiful artwork
  • 🐾 Animation scenes
  • 🐾 Relaxing music
  • 🐾 CG Gallery Mode
  • 🐾 Puzzle game

    In the game, your goal is to collect the puzzle in order to restore the pictures.
